section CommutativeLemmas

variable [CommSemiring R] [AddCommMonoid A] [AddCommMonoid B] [CovariantClass B B (· + ·) (· ≤ ·)]
  [CovariantClass B B (Function.swap (· + ·)) (· ≤ ·)] [AddCommMonoid T]
